                    <span>Slave Religion is a valuable text.  The author does an excellent presentation of the experiences of our ancestors prior to their departure from Africa and their arrival on the plantations. I use this text in a  course I teach, The History of the Black Church.  The author is to be  commended for his research.</span>
                  
